reviewText: Guys, I don't know what your life experiences have taught you, but plastic-looking C cups do not qualify as "bra busters"--that one reviewer couldn't possibly be more wrong. If you're looking for honestly big breasts, look somewhere else--I'd suggest something from Danni Ashe, anything with Glori-Anne Gilbert or Mary Carey, or even CandyGirl Video: Sweet Satisfaction Jasmine Grey [Special Edition]. Based on the title, this one is a big (no pun intended) disappointment. On its own merits, however, it's a fair production, made much better because of the inclusion of Shay Laren. She is FANTASTIC and her vignette alone is five stars. Jelena Jensen, while her vignette is not nearly as hot as Shay's (she appears to be pretty pudgy here), is the only other starlet featured who is naturally big busted. Take these two away and the only thing meritorious is the explicitness of the vignettes. No real complaints about that; plenty of full nudity with graphic shots below the waist.

This is a sexy Peach movie with lovely Heather Vandeven and Lela Star notably. They make me forget the others in it. Peach videos are quite sexy, and this is one of the better titles. I have bought many Peach DVDs from Amazon. I see previews that look as if the movies are good on Peach DVDs I already own and check these titles at Amazon that has allowed me to own many I wanted to find.

I've got quite many Peach DVDs, and this is one of my favorites! I don't know why the "Editorial Reviews" on this page says there are 5 ladies here, because there are actually 10: Zoe Britton, Lisa Daniels, Devon, Jelena Jensen, Shay Laren, Laura Lee, Brea Lynn, Lela Star, Lexxi Tyler, and Heather Vandeven. All 10 can fairly be described as knock-outs, and all of them live up to the title BRA BUSTERS, although none is monstrously stacked either. The entire DVD consists of the ladies stripping one at a time in various settings indoor and out, getting completely nude. However, although a few segments were shot outdoors, it doesn't appear that any of them is "public nudity." There is nothing explicit going on, even though the ladies are not shy about showing everything, so I imagine this would be rated R. Picture quality and camerawork are very good, with most segments in widescreen. One issue with many Peach DVDs is that the company often re-uses the same segments on various DVDs, so that I often end up with duplicates. I didn't already have any of BRA BUSTERS, though, so I don't know if any of these segments appear on other Peach DVDs or not. The main program runs a generous 75 minutes, with bonuses of a nice photo gallery that runs about 7 minutes, and trailers of 4 other Peach DVDs. Highly recommended!
